errorlogger
===========

Dump error message in `with` statement to file or sqlite.


Usage
-----

    from errorlogger import ErrorLogger
    
    # dump to file
    with ErrorLogger('log.txt'):
        do_something()

    # dump to sqlite    
    with ErrorLogger('log.db', 'sqlite'):
        do_something()


